{"tid":1711392,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[大韓民國萬歲] 首爾大學生「沉默遊行」聲援香港","createTime":"2019-11-12T11:26:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-13T02:01:52.000Z","uid":4574,"like":52,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"a12969f8928553fad878b1d624bcfbb9ee3d5b0f","tid":1711392,"uid":4574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T11:26:02.000Z","msg":"轉自蘋果新聞 <br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20191112/60257777?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR1KKxPEdRJ4BzRkxkrr1wuincXdtp7e9QiQ2QF7BjIuKqlZvvuKQpOylQE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191112%2F60257777%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR1KKxPEdRJ4BzRkxkrr1wuincXdtp7e9QiQ2QF7BjIuKqlZvvuKQpOylQE&d=9CaroZtPfqcCLVRp0XVEkfRe10cHvJvhFGsNMWslaGA%3D&h=6ab89394\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191112%2F60257777%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR1KKxPEdRJ4BzRkxkrr1wuincXdtp7e9QiQ2QF7BjIuKqlZvvuKQpOylQE&h=7a707348\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20191112/60257777?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR1KKxPEdRJ4BzRkxkrr1wuincXdtp7e9QiQ2QF7BjIuKqlZvvuKQpOylQE</a><br />\n<br />\n【抗暴之戰】首爾大學生「沉默遊行」聲援香港 抗議南韓政府未有發聲撐港人<br />\n<br />\n香港周一有交通警開實彈槍射傷手無寸鐵的示威學生，震驚國際社會，不過南韓政府數個月以來對香港問題保持沉默，當地有部份大學生用行動抗議當局沉默，有聲援香港的民眾慨嘆：「（南韓）政府和執政圈只看中國面色，而不理睬被鎮壓的香港市民。」<br />\n<br />\n報道指，包括國立首爾大學在內的部份大學學生最近用行動抗議當局沉默，首爾大學生周一身穿黑色服裝、佩戴黑色口罩，在校內「沉默遊行」。參加的大學生說，這場遊行有三重意義，<span style=\"color: red;\">一是為遭當局施以暴力而犧牲的人們默哀，二是表明立場與被剝奪言論自由的港人站在一起，三是批評中國政府和知道事實卻選擇沉默的南韓政府。</span>另外在上周六的一個集會，有團體讚揚香港民眾追求民主的熱情，認為南韓政府不能保持沉默。<br />\n<br />\n報道提及南韓政府對香港反送中事件僅表示「希望能和平解決」的原則性立場。南韓外交部在8月份的例行記者會上說：「期待當事人之間能夠圓滿解決。」指即使中國政府強硬手段對待香港示威，南韓也因顧及中國政府反應，態度含糊不清。南韓政壇幾乎不會提起香港示威，執政黨共同民主黨未曾發表相關評論，有黨中人說：「因為要考慮韓中關係惡化政治問題，有很多顧慮，所以事實上要小心翼翼的。」<br />\n<br />\n中央社／南韓《朝鮮日報》<br />\n<br />\n不愧係金義聖先生母校<br />\noppa onni saranghae  <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39341702b129e8c3ae6c57d29b479a1aff8d11cf","tid":1711392,"uid":305269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T11:26:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8e1fe654300a670f2c8f640383304d5c69bacbf","tid":1711392,"uid":37869,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T11:30:09.000Z","msg":"係時候團結全世界對付中國"},{"pid":"0dc09938bd78bb94124f7f39358a1621f8568467","tid":1711392,"uid":124711,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T11:53:18.000Z","msg":"Oppa<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e703958b8522179d7305ac499b12a69c4714e27","tid":1711392,"uid":286792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T11:58:39.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9a89798a6ea6d9a415c1585efa7d9523b85ec7e4","tid":1711392,"uid":34899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T23:05:55.000Z","msg":"感謝好國人"},{"pid":"39b1217e057cad1ae77d29760c071bf873b6adab","tid":1711392,"uid":258373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T23:12:08.000Z","msg":"Push."},{"pid":"71055e5b36498944b16e4586c49f51e204dee972","tid":1711392,"uid":197213,